Welcome to your dream home at 5155 Mayflower Street in beautiful Cocoa, Florida. This spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is the epitome of comfort and style, featuring a range of desirable amenities that will elevate your Florida living experience with NO HOA.Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a charming and well-maintained exterior, providing excellent curb appeal. As you step inside, the freshly painted walls create a warm and inviting atmosphere, making you feel right at home from the moment you enter.The heart of this home is the open-concept living area. This home features HVAC 2017, upgraded appliances, solar panels that are owned not leased and above ground pool.. This upgraded home is ready for you to move in and watch the rockets launched from KSC Welcome to your dream home at 5155 Mayflower Street in beautiful Cocoa, Florida. This spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is the epitome of comfort and style, featuring a range of desirable amenities that will elevate your Florida living experience.

Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a charming and well-maintained exterior, providing excellent curb appeal. As you step inside, the freshly painted walls create a warm and inviting atmosphere, making you feel right at home from the moment you enter.

The heart of this home is the open-concept living area, which seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. It's the perfect space for relaxing with family or entertaining friends. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a breakfast bar, ensuring that cooking and dining are both convenient and enjoyable.

This property is not only beautifully designed but also energy-efficient, with owned, not leased solar panels that significantly reduce your electric bills. Embrace the benefits of sustainable living while saving on utility costs.

Step outside, and you'll find a spacious and fenced-in backyard. It's a perfect oasis for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding in your private outdoor space.

The four well-appointed bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. The master suite features an en-suite bathroom, while the other bedrooms share a well-designed, second bathroom.

Situated in a desirable location in Cocoa, you'll have convenient access to local amenities, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Cocoa is known for its proximity to beautiful beaches, outdoor recreational opportunities, and a vibrant community.

Don't miss the chance to make 5155 Mayflower Street your new home in Cocoa, Florida. This property offers a rare combination of comfort, style, energy efficiency, and outdoor enjoyment. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this dream home yours!
